## Tappalka and posts

Canonical rules (eligibility, show-cost priority including `sourceEntityId` / `CommunityWallet`, stop-loss, `noAuthorWalletSpend`, win reward): **@business-tappalka.mdc**. tRPC: `tappalka.getPair`, `tappalka.submitChoice`, `tappalka.getProgress`, `tappalka.markOnboardingSeen`.

